<div class="WordSection1"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Honeywell Aerospace Singapore Pte.Ltd.</span><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><br />2 Loyang Crescent</span><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><br />508976 Singapore</span></div>
<div class="WordSection1">
<p><span style="color: black; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">July 27, 2015<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>
<p><span style="color: black; font-size: 16px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Dear Qatar Airways, </span></p>
<p style="line-height: 115%;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 115%; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Last month we shared with you our SAP transition plans for the Singapore Loyang Avionic R&amp;O site. And we promised to provide you updates along the way. We are excited to say that we are still progressing towards a Sept. 27<sup>th</sup>, 2015, transition date.</span></p>
<p style="line-height: 115%;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 115%; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">You<span style="color: black;"> may recall, the Singapore SAP transition will result in a change to the Honeywell legal entity. Although the Singapore Loyang Avionic repairs will be performed at the same site, you will need to update the supplier information in your internal systems. <br /> <br /> </span>To minimize order disruptions, here<span style="color: black;"> are the steps you&rsquo;ll want and need to take as a result of this change: <br /></span></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Update your internal purchasing, authorized supplier list and quality management system (QMS) to reflect this legal entity name change. A <a href="https://pages3.honeywell.com/rs/641-QIX-912/images/Singapore 60 Day Transition Preparation Checklist .pdf" target="_blank">transition checklist</a><span style="color: red;"> </span>is available and includes the new supplier address, amended &ldquo;Ship To&rdquo; address, and invoicing and payment bank details. </span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="color: black;">Execute a Novation Agreement to assign rights and obligations from Honeywell Aerospace Singapore Pte. Ltd. to </span>Honeywell International S&agrave;rl. Our Customer Business Manager and Contracts team have been in contact with your company to provide additional information to complete this action this month.</span></li>
</ul>
<span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">If you have any questions or concerns, please reach out to your Honeywell Customer Business Manager or email us at <a href="mailto:AeroCPSCommunications@Honeywell.com"><span style="color: windowtext; text-decoration: none;">AeroCPSCommunications@Honeywell.com</span></a>.<span style="color: black;"></span></span><br />
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Yours sincerely,</span></p>
<span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>Aileen McDowall</strong></span></div>
<div class="WordSection1"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Region Vice President AT&amp;R Airlines, EMEAI<br /></span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Honeywell International S&agrave;rl </span></div>
